OL,3,CRobert Rhodes jailed for life for
OL,4,Cwife's murder after re-trial
OL,6,FHe originally walked free for the
OL,7,Fmurder of his wife, 38, in 2017,
OL,8,Fhaving been found not guilty at the
OL,9,FOld Bailey, and it was only when new
OL,10,Fevidence - supplied by the couple's
OL,11,Fchild - appeared that he was able to
OL,12,Fbe re-trialed.
