OL,4,Cwife's murder after re-trial
OL,6,F"He maintains his innocence in these
OL,7,Fmatters and has refused to attend,"
OL,8,Fdefence barrister Nina Grahame KC told
OL,9,Fthe court before the sentencing.
OL,11,FAs well as the murder conviction,
OL,12,FRhodes was also found guilty in
OL,13,FDecember last year of two counts of
OL,14,Fperjury for false evidence at his Old
OL,15,FBailey trial and in the family courts
OL,16,Fin 2018, perverting the course of
OL,17,Fjustice, and child cruelty.
