OL,3,CRobert Rhodes jailed for life for
OL,4,Cwife's murder after re-trial
OL,6,FThe murder happened on June 2, 2016,
OL,7,Fwhen the couple's marriage had become
OL,8,Fdifficult, and Rhodes had filed for
OL,9,Fdivorce.
OL,11,FPolice received a 999 call from the
OL,12,Fchild at 7.34pm during which Rhodes
OL,13,Fsaid his wife had attacked him and
OL,14,Ftheir child with a knife.
OL,16,FDawn Rhodes was found lying on the
OL,17,Fkitchen floor at their home in
OL,18,FRedhill, Surrey, with her throat cut.
