OL,3,CRobert Rhodes jailed for life for
OL,4,Cwife's murder after re-trial
OL,6,FRobert Rhodes claimed to officers that
OL,7,Fhis wife had hit him twice on the back
OL,8,Fof the head, and later in his first
OL,9,Ftrial, he described her coming at him
OL,10,Fafter "flipping like a Hulk".
OL,12,FTo back up his claims, Rhodes had
OL,13,Fstabbed himself and inflicted a cut on
OL,14,Fthe child's arm ` wounds he blamed on
OL,15,Fhis wife.
OL,17,FRhodes thought he had got away with
OL,18,Fmurder when he was acquitted in 2017.
