OL,6,FWhen he was arrested for murder again,
OL,7,Fhe tellingly told officers he had
OL,8,F"thought this would come back to bite
OL,9,Fme".
OL,11,FHis acquittal on the murder charge was
OL,12,Fquashed in the Court of Appeal, and
OL,13,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service was
OL,14,Fgranted permission by senior judges to
OL,15,Fbring the case to a second trial.
